sentences: Sev Lewkowicz (born 15 February 1951, London, England) is a musical composer, producer, arranger and keyboard player based in the United Kingdom.
He has recorded and released four solo albums; No Such Thing As Silence (Centaur Discs 1997), Mariner (Centaur Discs 1998)  This Is Not the End (Lynchet Records 2006) and The War Poets (2018).
